# ⚡ 9. Performance upgrade (очень важно)

Сейчас у тебя “toy loop”. Делаем **почти production loop**.

---

## 🔁 Batch processing

```cpp
std::vector<Packet> batch;

while (running) {
    batch.clear();

    for (int i = 0; i < 32; ++i) {
        batch.push_back(generate_packet());
    }

    for (auto& pkt : batch) {
        pkt.mark_ingress();
        pipeline.process(pkt);
    }
}
```

👉 Это:

* уменьшает syscall overhead
* улучшает cache locality

---

## 🧵 10. Thread model (минимум)

```text
Thread 1: RX / generate packets
Thread 2: pipeline processing
Thread 3: TCP link
```

---

# 🔒 11. Lock-free queue (минимальный вариант)

## utils/spsc_queue.h (упрощённый)

```cpp
#pragma once
#include <atomic>
#include <vector>

template<typename T>
class SPSCQueue {
public:
    explicit SPSCQueue(size_t size)
        : buffer_(size) {}

    bool push(const T& item) {
        auto next = (head_ + 1) % buffer_.size();
        if (next == tail_) return false;

        buffer_[head_] = item;
        head_ = next;
        return true;
    }

    bool pop(T& item) {
        if (tail_ == head_) return false;

        item = buffer_[tail_];
        tail_ = (tail_ + 1) % buffer_.size();
        return true;
    }

private:
    std::vector<T> buffer_;
    size_t head_{0};
    size_t tail_{0};
};
```

